<subSubSection pageId="139" pageNumber="899" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="139.[1410,2620,741,1642]" pageId="139" pageNumber="899">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1410,1644,1214,1247]" pageId="139" pageNumber="899">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Call shape is steep FM sweep, with start frequencies of 132-184-8 kHz (mean 173-1 kHz), end frequencies of 67-2-96-8 kHz (77-1 kHz), peak frequencies of 83-2-137-6 kHz (101-4 kHz), and durations of 0-7-3 milliseconds (1-7 milliseconds).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
